				<title><![CDATA[I Did Bicep Push-Ups Every Day For 30 Days — You’ll Be Surprised By The Results]]></title>
				<link>https://www.endomondo.com/training/bicep-push-up-benefits-after-a-month</link>
				<guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.endomondo.com/?post_type=informational_posts&#038;p=34967</guid>
				<pubDate>Tue, 14 Jan 2025 02:37:14 +0000				</pubDate>
				<dc:creator><![CDATA[Chris Marshall, MSc, PT]]></dc:creator>
