				<title><![CDATA[I Did Handstand Push-Ups Every Day For A Month — What I Observed]]></title>
				<link>https://www.endomondo.com/training/handstand-push-up-benefits-after-a-month</link>
				<guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.endomondo.com/?post_type=informational_posts&#038;p=35674</guid>
				<pubDate>Tue, 14 Jan 2025 02:18:54 +0000				</pubDate>
				<dc:creator><![CDATA[Chris Marshall, MSc, PT]]></dc:creator>
